# 2026-07-09 09:16:20.793292
+Refactor and clean up sarmkadan/dotnet-feature-flags.
+Work in: /home/redrocket/task-factory/workdir/dotnet-feature-flags
+
+1. Review code for obvious improvements:
+   - Extract long methods (>30 lines) into smaller focused methods
+   - Replace magic numbers/strings with constants
+   - Apply async/await consistently (no .Result or .Wait())
+   - Use pattern matching where appropriate
+   - Use string interpolation instead of concatenation
+2. Apply nullable reference types if not enabled (#nullable enable)
+3. Add sealed keyword to classes not designed for inheritance
+4. Keep changes minimal and safe - no architectural changes
+
